         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Menches, komogrammateus of Kerkeosiris, from Apollodoros, the contractor for the retailing and the tax upon oil at the same village for the 4th year. My tax-farming contract Ö into extraordinary poverty because of those who are smuggling into the village and illicitly selling contraband oil and kiki Ö (here the papyrus breaks off)</ab>
         </div>
